# AI Code Rate Marker Rule

When you output AI-generated code snippets, you must wrap the code payload with the exact markers below so it can be counted for AI-rate statistics:

```text
###start###
AI代码
AI代码
AI代码
###end###
```

Requirements:
- Always include `###start###` and `###end###` on separate lines.
- Place only the AI-generated code content between the markers.
- Do not omit or rename these markers.
- If no code is produced, do not output this wrapper.
